tactics.stateBefore:
α : Type u_1
i : Nat
a' : α
l : List α
h : i < l.length
⊢ ∃ l₁ l₂, l = l₁ ++ l[i] :: l₂ ∧ l₁.length = i ∧ l.set i a' = l₁ ++ a' :: l₂
tactics.stateAfter:
α : Type u_1
i : Nat
a' : α
l : List α
h : i < l.length
⊢ l.set i a' = take i l ++ a' :: drop (i + 1) l

α : Type u_1
xs : Array α
i : USize
d : α
h : i.toNat < xs.size
⊢ ∃ l₁ l₂, xs.toList = l₁ ++ xs[i] :: l₂ ∧ l₁.length = i.toNat ∧ (xs.uset i d h).toList = l₁ ++ d :: l₂
